Name: UNDYED TOWELLING SWEATSHIRT
Size: ['Small (PRE-ORDER ships between 21-25 May)', 'Medium (PRE-ORDER ships between 21-25 May)', 'Large (PRE-ORDER ships between 21-25 May)']
Description: Oversized, lightweight, and undyed sweater made of 100% organic cotton. The undyed collection is more than a way to avoid waste (dyeing cotton has more impact than dyeing any other fabric). It is a link to authenticity expressed in the minimalist but timeless aesthetic of unprocessed cotton. An estimated 8,000 synthetic chemicals are used to bleach, treat, and brighten clothes, with 17% to 20% of industrial water pollution resulting from fabric dyes and textile finishings. Using this fabric saves 80 liters of water per kilogram of jersey fabric produced. Sustainable packaged.
